  "prompt": "How do I collect movie tickets booked on BookMyShow?",
  "response": "To collect movie tickets booked on BookMyShow, you typically have several options:\n\n1. E-Ticket Option:\n- Most theaters now accept digital tickets\n- Open the BookMyShow app or website\n- Go to \"My Bookings\" section\n- Display the e-ticket/QR code at the theater entrance\n- No physical ticket printing required\n\n2. Print-at-Home Tickets:\n- Log in to BookMyShow website\n- Go to \"My Bookings\"\n- Select the specific movie booking\n- Click \"Print Ticket\" option\n- Print the ticket and carry it to the theater\n\n3. Ticket Counter Collection:\n- Carry a valid ID proof\n- Carry the booking confirmation (SMS/email)\n- Go to the theater's ticket counter\n- Provide booking details or booking reference number\n- Collect physical tickets\n\n4. Mobile Ticket:\n- Open BookMyShow mobile app\n- Go to \"My Bookings\"\n- Select the movie ticket\n- Show the digital ticket with QR code at entry\n\nTips:\n- Arrive at the theater early\n- Ensure your phone is charged\n- Check specific theater's ticket collection policy\n- Carry ID proof for verification",
